{"id": "ChIJH92kKx7HwoARRV2xuwL-NuY", "rating": 3.7, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 360, "displayName": {"text": "About Time", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJH92kKx7HwoARRV2xuwL-NuY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSbWFXRlBkMmhCU0RKM1QyVm9ja2huY1VacmVVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "About Time is easily one of the cutest cafes I’ve been to in Ktown and one of the only cafes open until late night. The space is super aesthetic and cozy with plenty of seating, making it perfect for studying, working, catching up with friends, or just romanticizing your life for a few hours.\n\nI loved their specialty drinks and desserts… everything looked so pretty and tasted amazing. My favorites were definitely the Basque cheesecake, Dubai chocolate cake, and their Spanish latte! so good and perfect for a late night cafe run.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "About Time is easily one of the cutest cafes I’ve been to in Ktown and one of the only cafes open until late night. The space is super aesthetic and cozy with plenty of seating, making it perfect for studying, working, catching up with friends, or just romanticizing your life for a few hours.\n\nI loved their specialty drinks and desserts… everything looked so pretty and tasted amazing. My favorites were definitely the Basque cheesecake, Dubai chocolate cake, and their Spanish latte! so good and perfect for a late night cafe run.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "CM YEMIMA", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115137950788251240478/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbF5QOJM4yuMn6KgaZXqJCHCrWBlj6zlpT2IDf9T6WS-BIwbRK=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-22T20:04:51.054009065Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSbWFXRlBkMmhCU0RKM1QyVm9ja2huY1VacmVVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSbWFXRlBkMmhCU0RKM1QyVm9ja2huY1VacmVVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c71e2ba4dd1f:0xe636fe02bbb15d45"}, {"name": "places/ChIJH92kKx7HwoARRV2xuwL-NuY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KTGN6Tk9TRE5wWDNoalZYTkJUWFl5VURCdFRIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Great food, awesome drinks. The cafe latte was slightly unusual in the great unique sense. Free wifi available with quite a password. Comfortable and cozy seating available in two levels, both very aesthetic for pictures and posts. Upper level seating closes at 12, so we were told to move down but seating was full so we left. Great spacious cafe, will return.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great food, awesome drinks. The cafe latte was slightly unusual in the great unique sense. Free wifi available with quite a password. Comfortable and cozy seating available in two levels, both very aesthetic for pictures and posts. Upper level seating closes at 12, so we were told to move down but seating was full so we left. Great spacious cafe, will return.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "jkus eats", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114925381811192573107/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXs9Jp5sWxU7-R9i7J7GJnADo5t6nNEU6ahdMFAPmZvHO_O4r4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-29T02:02:50.706270654Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KTGN6Tk9TRE5wWDNoalZYTkJUWFl5VURCdFRIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KTGN6Tk9TRE5wWDNoalZYTkJUWFl5VURCdFRIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c71e2ba4dd1f:0xe636fe02bbb15d45"}, {"name": "places/ChIJH92kKx7HwoARRV2xuwL-NuY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWdFZXZFhWVzVQUjNKVFMzRmtZWFpEWjJadmVHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Rec: Matcha Einspanner\nGot the Matcha Einspanner and Yuzu Peach Green Tea. Matcha Einspanner was nothing special, but good. Yuzu Peach Green Tea is $6 but even with added honey, doesn’t taste good. Very pricey drinks, even for LA, $9 for a drink (matcha Einspanner) and no free parking. Parking guy was friendly and thankfully I didn’t get the cashier that many others have gotten. Cashier was friendly. I was there on a Sunday, so lots of people, very crowded.\n01/25/2026", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Rec: Matcha Einspanner\nGot the Matcha Einspanner and Yuzu Peach Green Tea. Matcha Einspanner was nothing special, but good. Yuzu Peach Green Tea is $6 but even with added honey, doesn’t taste good. Very pricey drinks, even for LA, $9 for a drink (matcha Einspanner) and no free parking. Parking guy was friendly and thankfully I didn’t get the cashier that many others have gotten. Cashier was friendly. I was there on a Sunday, so lots of people, very crowded.\n01/25/2026", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Xue", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110925827671659266422/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqSBzVgQJQdqTn8tWsjt84hLalJLk3cMCDk-BGBJJ0EHCLHw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-27T22:55:35.388448017Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWdFZXZFhWVzVQUjNKVFMzRmtZWFpEWjJadmVHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWdFZXZFhWVzVQUjNKVFMzRmtZWFpEWjJadmVHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c71e2ba4dd1f:0xe636fe02bbb15d45"}, {"name": "places/ChIJH92kKx7HwoARRV2xuwL-NuY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrM1FYTjFNSFJJVERneFUxUnhVekU0ZW05eWIyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Had the pistachio latte and a blueberry muffin, and both were delicious! The atmosphere was great - very cozy, vibrant, and full of good vibes. There’s plenty of seating, making it a nice spot to relax, work, or catch up with friends.\n\nThe only thing to keep in mind is parking. Since it’s located on Main Street, finding a spot can be a bit challenging at busy times. You may need to use nearby paid parking. Other than that, it was a wonderful experience, and I’d definitely come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had the pistachio latte and a blueberry muffin, and both were delicious! The atmosphere was great - very cozy, vibrant, and full of good vibes. There’s plenty of seating, making it a nice spot to relax, work, or catch up with friends.\n\nThe only thing to keep in mind is parking. Since it’s located on Main Street, finding a spot can be a bit challenging at busy times. You may need to use nearby paid parking. Other than that, it was a wonderful experience, and I’d definitely come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Barathwaja S", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103123007370229635086/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRZasbln-GJywvnzwXCTZvvrtLAhBALNYTUNOHBJrnk-MU-ru8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-01T05:54:45.808469056Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrM1FYTjFNSFJJVERneFUxUnhVekU0ZW05eWIyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrM1FYTjFNSFJJVERneFUxUnhVekU0ZW05eWIyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c71e2ba4dd1f:0xe636fe02bbb15d45"}, {"name": "places/ChIJH92kKx7HwoARRV2xuwL-NuY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaTGJEZzNOVTFXV1UxRWNESkpPRGRVYUdWR05VRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Super cute aesthetic and a nice patio when the weather doesn’t suck. However the seats are limited unless you’re there basically when they open. There are also like zero plugs. One of those LA coffee shops that doesn’t want you to get comfy.\n\nThe corn latte is great. There is a parking lot but it does fill up. They have a lot of food options, mostly vegetarian sandwiches, soups, and some very delicious cakes.\n\nFour stars bc the coffee and the snacks are great, the fight for seating, parking and plugs make this better for meeting friends than serious working.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Super cute aesthetic and a nice patio when the weather doesn’t suck. However the seats are limited unless you’re there basically when they open. There are also like zero plugs. One of those LA coffee shops that doesn’t want you to get comfy.\n\nThe corn latte is great. There is a parking lot but it does fill up. They have a lot of food options, mostly vegetarian sandwiches, soups, and some very delicious cakes.\n\nFour stars bc the coffee and the snacks are great, the fight for seating, parking and plugs make this better for meeting friends than serious working.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Simone Egwu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105845565587956142858/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFKgwiEGzcVeSveKn-T1DSXYONCxOr1DzyYVxcbFvpFwTsCzpt=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-17T20:28:47.058933992Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaTGJEZzNOVTFXV1UxRWNESkpPRGRVYUdWR05VRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaTGJEZzNOVTFXV1UxRWNESkpPRGRVYUdWR05VRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c71e2ba4dd1f:0xe636fe02bbb15d45"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJH92kKx7HwoARRV2xuwL-NuY/photos/AWCwydgyQaKRffCrgqUSNsULa0iANrvDV5sPsuNSZmzuWpK3CiAwzyYInlYjUAU6M7XWbuFlnBJjVXFTjJubN_ykEVuS95AKBEjcbs-BrvzGu4c2irrOUjqDyNs4NmznMXQiW0vvInoR